snippet.title: Drift Vector Trailer
snippet.description:
Hi! I'm Biggles! I've never had a YouTube channel before, but this is a trailer for a little synthwave shooty spaceship game I'm working on at the moment called Drift Vector.

It's still quite early in development but there's currently a free demo available for PC & Mac you can check out!
